code: @Override protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     URI url = new URI(uri).     // must use copy as each endpoint can have different options     ObjectHelper.notNull(configuration, "configuration").     GangliaConfiguration config = configuration.copy().     config.configure(url).     setProperties(config, parameters).     GangliaEndpoint endpoint = new GangliaEndpoint(uri, this).     endpoint.setConfiguration(config).     setProperties(endpoint, parameters).     return endpoint. }
/**  * To use the shared configuration  */ public void setConfiguration(GangliaConfiguration configuration) {     this.configuration = configuration. }
